    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to be listing this absolute beauty today. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept in a garage, so the paint is flawless and the interior is pristine. If you're looking for a ride that's practically perfect, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary mechanical concerns. The chassis maintains its original factory kinematics with impeccable hydraulic steering feedback. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep luster with zero evidence of oxidation or panel misalignment. A mechanically flawless example of the ultimate driving machine.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Flawless interior. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age, maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state; the premium leather still carries its original factory scent, and every surface\u2014from the pristine carpeting to the unblemished dashboard\u2014is free of wear. Mechanically, this car is flawless, featuring a complete, documented service history with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage is as immaculate as the bodywork. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
